{"tid":1978413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見連登仔成日屌人熱狗 想講一句","createTime":"2020-04-18T16:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T17:08:13.000Z","uid":216008,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2230c88ac426c168054884b7210c353af96173b9","tid":1978413,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:38:26.000Z","msg":"其實政黨有小圈子好正常<br />\n但其實而家係要香港人槍頭對外<br />\n話就話大家行緊唔同山<br />\n問題係你座山登唔到 就可以登佢嗰棟<br />\nthere should be always plan B, C, D.....<br />\n今日拉左15個民主派 你可以話白頭佬之流抵死<br />\n但拉闊睇 呢個係白色恐佈 <br />\n同時間大家仲鬧緊邊個會員係熱狗 邊個係偽黃<br />\n學我中學阿sir講<br />\nDo the right thing at the right time<br />\n唔洗應承我 唔洗打口號<br />\n搵啲野做 吸收多啲知識 做多啲體能<br />\n有緣會見"},{"pid":"ab1649399b6e1b847f9ac08d7d45db1a599dcfb2","tid":1978413,"uid":173849,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:42:55.000Z","msg":"熱狗分化撚，日日倡白票，依家先想洗底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea794bebc7aa22e71ba1fdf1830eeae5ff3a6b0","tid":1978413,"uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MDU58B7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMDU58B7.jpg&h=2764b124&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6dc8899124a926e17aea414623d964382aa58d01","tid":1978413,"uid":227801,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:49:46.000Z","msg":"團結除熱狗外嘅人"},{"pid":"d51e96245ec4e32acfffef14f65e0813ed517e59","tid":1978413,"uid":35860,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T17:08:13.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山喎，熱狗同踢人落山有咩分別？<br />\n樓主又會唔會屌柒班踢同路人落山既仆街？"}]}